lt;/a&gt;，包括乌克兰在该国内最大胆的空中袭击之一。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SgUiXJvQjXMgUrq-fbAwQ7zknJQ-4YBC6c26vuQxcr9FoYT202KdFYoXjjWKTDWySMh6r19vixBrwUuHExTFyBlJaoUcx-gQQCw60gStkfhUsnQ4Z-k670wpRIC_K5UlN7buCkOrl0NpMYQ35dZq44_EkW0pU_r2pj5kTqkW2Gz_Jw4rssaNctpvK5MGs0Yl_wk0sLJ1uW-7lfVQ9fWWovbahcorMZNDpBz08E4md900NwwVtFpQiJGTXik2LfckN_wahLPCiIDBJoiPTlPb8gm0oQ/5CTy38DL9iKBgtyklLDM7-J4UvKtjNQZ/9" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieXDHUj6DHiQ/v1/550x381.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img class="email-ssl-image" height="381" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieXDHUj6DHiQ/v1/550x381.jpg" style="border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; width: 550px; height: 381px;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/96WFk-tu3s4FpXJTYOupDaUYiWTCMXpcdYkkUuZ2Vmw3ZUvPIQfCT-5lVp1mVFd8iozl7zDfVPyE0rSJS1oNybQLp8CA1Jvq1W6w8PJ8xuqQkJIxTcLlR5MaqpZfh2caV1pMpN1KKCnY37NfncvUAHWrB0JC7MfWInXSEzgLX1bPTSYfOZ_V2xOsV1kDrAYyyIXQomlUmsSQWTMlyLFzfrZXEwgSmcyMou__32tlusIQo9Mg1atxOcbsNUpjcp74xE_2ZYW155u0ykg5Wy8bNoZkcQ/JM_psH5wEt6diAedjvw4Lmu86QD_b6az/9" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_bla