t;em&gt;零&lt;/em&gt;，Akshat Rathi与制片人奥斯卡·博伊德（Oscar Boyd）坐下来，焦点令人惊讶的罪魁祸首减慢了过渡： &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/T8QSKQg8dEVSkqdmnidi72V83OvIApMjAWJ3otF7_rBwmim30H2xTjFkM5nL0Oh9ImrEGNbtcPbYXQCr74QBcWnDe4joCE2O_eTB2oC-uN9hPxT0qHgBRloaQsVm0u_AFNDozrBgcd5D8aScINSrXgsEexdSmlYG_oZmVPX24_pMD7HVFRUSsFyVq7KUgWRExB0QurK77oPTDTzPK2jZHeXh1sdjUZRlday8K9GyqPOA2auiniX3_nX7VXKD44nQgr2awjBnxrqOX5UQVWAqTwCcmQ/I3Dpm0L-X_4-7cngxctg0szaPZ_i3eG6/9" target="_blank"&gt;全球变形金刚短缺&lt;/a&gt;，以及为什么它使行业内部人士如此担心。这一集启动了&lt;em&gt;瓶颈&lt;/em&gt;，这是一个新系列，探索了鲜为人知的障碍，阻碍了我们充满活力的未来。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yfX4v5e62EsM_lzuhB0IAkvO0_pxpmJciYhtjBAnw7_6alFclc8zhSjDn4OV5XgOCL8CTlcpphtGD8qzpZYu6PtGbBbKZmClp6rLfO-vqbcrbmL0QLJl_siEuvZb2-1JX0T0Dv99FSWUwQ33cwTbDjTGojPrPxVPGnMsoH1ckB7pzo1t8qnAFZ46_84ES5SyY18DLSnmiv_KmxM6YVOrzm-lqvhF6DUfU4c2x89nlPyTqUWuWbkyuWhpXR_gQDDuvf2_-Ltf_9SxnZMb-vCe5b_wiSSqmtbhGi3sd_Uo1Bn99K-dg0_brjgpMYj8ruHPEHg/ZcUOnu4AggqEBg2WIy_pMv7J_6zOOcUo/9" target="_blank" title="设备促进了世界电气化的未来：瓶颈系列"&gt;立即收听&lt;/a&gt;，然后在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/wBVLzkuCN0LuUKYIS7fDXBl14UK-UzvtFBFMe5pM5qpji34IlHcn8ha9NK6WQwc-yfPjVezfdTmVTjDuBTgjIaIHxggi7qV6x1gH6pwpb_Hi1Rf2wuKhU8mOz6qWHvZvPCOrjHAEFQbi9W2GfnDC8Q3YHbV1VqQOsL5_j9Fg_gZvwupa-JjgP_gzbACPt5xC2E_pQ2p8L4j7a9_xa8ciK-IcyQRW9KalOz652YLb8yW2GJj43RnFP-Ah3_KREmEEg7XzmGtHHfSjX7MulpmQ91ieqvqWOAtQgpeaPGKYrTfi5ASahk4U5EINz55H4YTWOQJaNg/CfzwQMVgS-iN0BT3P49Yh3PpRyrVdSG5/9" target="_blank"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; ， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lvVi4QAgbSUiDTHxx2CfFBLQAC102LJLttj3PspdVnA3oacuB3cEFNtsJzCpAJywNL08PwcHHuDoO3q1MV91itoKat_KlKpinVImczqX7qRR6j6Z36OydGWwIlL4fKrFwPEEfZ8P9LqROCaAT7MU566VRQcs3oEj116jAraFUnAAoVd4kTDkGFIeorhkj99FO_6W_TVCGGA4oPIKxtOUDg-kpNa7pFxib9iUnuUPYfnjlKJXcptov6DGCDOiuFxwdvv8nZZMHAU0WbGWEVYsMEQMyinL_QNLwsV30JhgmTrfQL78VN1jBF6SzXWSYS62Yq9VKmzMM7QvkDHo0yr0Vt_QrU9K/u20KgVQBvXo0IROqcxfjhmLk6d-ldjfu/9" target="_blank"&gt;Spotify&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href="https://links.mess