rif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;彭博绿色西雅图：&lt;/strong&gt; 7月14日至16日加入我们进行两天的引人入胜的对话，我们将探讨当今的紧急环境挑战以及明天的创新想法。特色演讲者包括巴塔哥尼亚首席执行官瑞安·盖勒特（Ryan Gellert），奥斯卡奖获奖演员简·方达（Jane Fonda）等等。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/CtP8xen3P29vFBCG8lcR8qGzK1NZy-aNhEcFhdAian5odVS-XUs_umuo8hXT9DxQufF1E1YF6Y4Vk6np4EWkeSPnNfCTld834NBuGJMFwCtLQbEeHdLaYYRLVwuevIrbA_pz9VXrzfLB8uNE3nSCilv6ExXST3qarZOhGx1X5BQZ_UTT63alv86Ih8hz1cFhRb6UOsbzkL1K-3Yvzjgi_3smrCLWsyvikQtVKXWdx91r29zm0S_EYv8n0eSfPJ67-FVJvVgwagiZEcWwXz7GH6u_KxotPcBg_q55zBpxOHfZ0bCMP0vqmCw7upNlHXbiViS_iwe5xnNL_ClcH-Yqee_3EgqWqXDvO_p-RrA55II8c1qNjcAiM4Qhv4fdeXN6LDg6cg9-HuXF2jHfrGrBA-f_26hx-sMOoDGT2ZdYCxT3wGo2PI9d1BpFNJHch9U_pubwKH8FxbTA0jxSwttZiFIJVYv2TVoXhQ/BZfefz74-GH_dybsOc79FMvvAsmZV0HO/9" target="_blank"&gt;单击此处以获取详细信息&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/pxuzvXRWbVycVSOMvvypCiMGhWIRalqGI7IIOb6OsjkR6b6AfjEdbhvw3gYktwmaXvY1sOiivvoQ2lbocSXzZ7vaKd2vK1VXMBmFGO-0hPq0vOEKndCvKb3lUTYkE8Rrgyt5cJ3QADg2h_iXscCf1Fg8iKXLci_9m6mzNo0COCZCX_vyjSJ61mIRjrT2X0QTROK2HU3qSB5deoEsmgX_Ah5KcpclaUYNrsjZlsUwmHs6Hcx8-vYd8E-MfeHjbVZXLetVxUXuHgq1QmyLatRP4_puuvsp2Ay6CI4K-gqMtZ7iGJsNG_ik2K3ng6FEHa7weHxZt0qDbXAFr2ryflaaBRW8o-fG51cfu6ceWl-8Z_sF3-fsAU2YoYpN4C9gnoUXghNInvykzCzEqY6mw0Z2kuIDncj-6krtk2sNCUkiTABkUe_a7bKJt1-qBiydfjjrp0gYAiP1uQ/DlfmPE8jZD_oIPoxY1ap26GW-kjqHbdj/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" border="0" class="lihide" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1099764&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=desktop&amp;amp;collapse_width=550&amp;amp;li=13733090&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=06022025&amp;amp;lctg=8b37da73-f2d1