，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;同一技术巨头&lt;/strong&gt;帮助将标准普尔500标准普尔500拖到熊市的边缘正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7l4ysxIQlT4y49LjFyD1mOxEO4Y2P4M8h7B5TjYKrMJDjQFO82Fum9wiFAyUYUtePsdG3qypzIvcegrQmVt2yXpSX-Sbd7Xs1jFa-XjyIG9dh1XwEpEAWuRCgLblJZ7xtGqTxWJKVKOcswlakxtgGv2z8Pjcumvq-qp2iuWBn0SlXnYdnlk7k8bokF8DEUjdXxyo5WehCDLJF21JhmUtm-DF1_7x_gEvwzKwsQoTfq9JW6pyxoWvHojcuIqcQAcKmQaLHbl6-GSZO4pd6bWAXVhsjg/2MoGlcSe88gDu4t0QoFsYg6uNU0sp4wO/9" target="_blank"&gt;为复苏提供动力&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;上周， &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Nvidia&lt;/strong&gt;在Big Tech的收入季节超过预期的收入季节，通过赢得了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qsfOlqAYJGt4d7J14IUxGMzenSw_q0j_Q43VYUWNlxtvj2JNlcOYG-jbhrMmjErCm2RON5KeUWLUqnBL7Az8dCsiR7eMkxIwk1y9y4KR2j8wKZPREcv1jX-xRAAsG7f6saVp4dHDIQnwUtMmMQI51EaX6MIYN3ZFhjlcIEZuz_yGIAVfZjbIdi_jwg-NsCtCEwjzfLPTQmFY-IwQUEqSyxbkUroiaKVIi6O7JXi62y2V0ZuVnZtC4O7ujUGrVMjC4GVPmIIMotDOCJiKa9y8POYSIg/60DuMr2G5JOlJXnAXqkEweKCNwjHwiBd/9" target="_blank"&gt;强劲的收入前景&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;随着NVIDIA和MICROSOFT&lt;/strong&gt;逐渐回到近记录，交易员正在押注该集团有望取消更广泛的市场。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;首先，富兰克林首席市场策略师布雷特·尤因（Brett Ewing）说&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;：“这个坦克中还有&lt;/strong&gt;更多的汽油。”&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;彭博观点的&lt;/strong&gt;乔纳森·莱文（Jonathan Levin）在下面解释了为什么标准普尔500指数正在通过特朗普政策动荡巡游。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/h2IThQjZEIDdOdgILpo5khgUTJGJ8rbzMUnlO1WFTfkS_Y72y8gd0ERnYHz41oeGjx5Dt-KE0zfAxsLqkY7cR2dSSJ1ROlKe5uTrbSXpdYGx2OBstc_1SCC2dpkpCqySMF6xe78ZxcNk